<h1 class="doc-page-title">Accessibility Management</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Comprehensive accessibility management for products including accessibility statements, issue tracking, WCAG compliance monitoring, and audit history.</p>

<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

<p>Accessibility management in COMPASS enables product teams to track and manage accessibility compliance for their products. This includes managing accessibility statements, tracking accessibility issues, monitoring WCAG compliance, and maintaining audit history.</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card border-primary h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-universal-access text-primary"></i> Product enrollment</h3>
                <p class="small mb-0">Enroll products for accessibility management and tracking.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card border-danger h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-danger"></i> Issue tracking</h3>
                <p class="small mb-0">Track accessibility issues with WCAG criteria linking and resolution.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card border-info h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check text-info"></i> WCAG compliance</h3>
                <p class="small mb-0">Monitor compliance with WCAG standards and track progress.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card border-success h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-history text-success"></i> Audit history</h3>
